(42, 12, 34, 40, 6, 21, 21, 'there will your heart be also', 'Connection of Heart and Treasure', 'Both passages emphasize the relationship between treasure and the heart, suggesting that one''s priorities and affections are reflected in what they value. This connection highlights a consistent teaching on the importance of where one places their treasure.', 'theme', 0.419, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 12, 34, 51, 3, 1, 3, 'there will your heart be also', 'Connection of Affection and Treasure', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of focusing one''s heart and affections on spiritual rather than earthly matters. Luke 12:34 highlights where one''s treasure is, while Colossians 3:2 urges believers to set their affection on things above.', 'theme', 0.419, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
