(42, 12, 35, 40, 25, 4, 10, 'your lights burning', 'Readiness for the Bridegroom', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of being prepared and vigilant. In Luke, the call to have ''your lights burning'' parallels the need for the wise virgins to have oil for their lamps in Matthew.', 'theme', 0.426, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
