(42, 12, 35, 23, 5, 27, 27, NULL, 'Readiness and Vigilance Theme', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of being prepared and alert. The imagery of girding loins and maintaining light in Luke parallels the readiness depicted in Isaiah, where none are weary or asleep.', 'theme', 0.40499999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
